 Verification: `grep \"informer-path\" hack/update-codegen.sh`\n38: \n39: - [ ] **T1.5**: Add lister-path parameter for listers output\n40:   - Purpose: Generate listers in client-go/listers/runtime/v1alpha1/\n41:   - File: `hack/update-codegen.sh`\n42:   - Verification: `grep \"lister-path\" hack/update-codegen.sh`\n43: \n44: - [ ] **T1.6**: Add --with-watch flag to generate watch-capable clients\n45:   - Purpose: Enable Watch method in typed clients\n46:   - File: `hack/update-codegen.sh`\n47:   - Verification: `grep \"with-watch\" hack/update-codegen.sh`\n48: \n49: - [ ] **T1.7**: Add API group version specification runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1\n50:   - Purpose: Specify correct API group for generation\n51:   - File: `hack/update-codegen.sh`\n52:   - Verification: `grep \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\" hack/update-codegen.sh || grep \"runtime/v1alpha1\" hack/update-codegen.sh`\n53: \n54: - [ ] **T1.8**: Add output-pkg parameter for module path\n55:   - Purpose: Set correct module import path github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go\n56:   - File: `hack/update-codegen.sh`\n57:   - Verification: `grep \"output-pkg=github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go\" hack/update-codegen.sh`\n58: \n59: ### Phase 2: Boilerplate Header File (ST-2)\n60: \n61: - [ ] **T2.1**: Create hack/boilerplate.go.txt header file\n62:   - Purpose: Provide copyright header template for generated code\n63:   - File: `hack/boilerplate.go.txt`\n64:   - Verification: `test -f hack/boilerplate.go.txt`\n65: \n66: - [ ] **T2.2**: Add copyright year placeholder in boilerplate\n67:   - Purpose: Use dynamic year for copyright headers\n68:   - File: `hack/boilerplate.go.txt`\n69:   - Verification: `grep \"YEAR\" hack/boilerplate.go.txt`\n70: \n71: - [ ] **T2.3**: Add Apache 2.0 license header in boilerplate\n72:   - Purpose: Include license information in generated code\n73:   - File: `hack/boilerplate.go.txt`\n74:   - Verification: `grep \"Apache License\" hack/boilerplate.go.txt`\n75: \n76: 