et/versioned/scheme/register.go`\n158:   - Verification: `grep \"var Codecs\" client-go/clientset/versioned/scheme/register.go`\n159: \n160: - [ ] **T4.10**: Verify AddToScheme function exists\n161:   - Purpose: Confirm scheme registration function\n162:   - File: `client-go/clientset/versioned/scheme/register.go`\n163:   - Verification: `grep \"AddToScheme\" client-go/clientset/versioned/scheme/register.go`\n164: \n165: ### Phase 5: Generate Typed Clients (ST-5)\n166: \n167: - [ ] **T5.1**: Verify runtime_client.go exists\n168:   - Purpose: Confirm RuntimeV1alpha1Client generated\n169:   - File: `client-go/clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/runtime_client.go`\n170:   - Verification: `test -f client-go/clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/runtime_client.go`\n171: \n172: - [ ] **T5.2**: Verify RuntimeV1alpha1Interface has RESTClient method\n173:   - Purpose: Confirm REST client accessor\n174:   - File: `client-go/clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/runtime_client.go`\n175:   - Verification: `grep \"RESTClient()\" client-go/clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/runtime_client.go`\n176: \n177: - [ ] **T5.3**: Verify agentruntime.go exists\n178:   - Purpose: Confirm AgentRuntime typed client generated\n179:   - File: `client-go/clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go`\n180:   - Verification: `test -f client-go/clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go`\n181: \n182: - [ ] **T5.4**: Verify AgentRuntimeInterface has Create method\n183:   - Purpose: Confirm Create operation supported\n184:   - File: `client-go/clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go`\n185:   - Verification: `grep \"Create(ctx\" client-go/clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go`\n186: \n187: - [ ] **T5.5**: Verify AgentRuntimeInterface has Update method\n188:   - Purpose: Confirm Update operation supported\n189:   - File: `client-go/clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go`\n190:   - Verifica