ern\n813: \n814: ```go\n815: lister := factory.Runtime().V1alpha1().AgentRuntimes().Lister()\n816: \n817: // List all in namespace\n818: arList, err := lister.AgentRuntimes(\"my-ns\").List(labels.Everything())\n819: \n820: // Get specific resource\n821: ar, err := lister.AgentRuntimes(\"my-ns\").Get(\"my-agentruntime\")\n822: ```\n823: \n824: ### Fake Clientset Usage Pattern\n825: \n826: ```go\n827: fakeClient := fake.NewSimpleClientset(\n828:     &runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime{\n829:         ObjectMeta: metav1.ObjectMeta{Name: \"test-ar\", Namespace: \"default\"},\n830:     },\n831: )\n832: \n833: // Test CRUD operations\n834: ar, err := fakeClient.RuntimeV1alpha1().AgentRuntimes(\"default\").Get(ctx, \"test-ar\", metav1.GetOptions{})\n835: ```\n836: \n837: ---\n838: \n839: ## Implementation Timeline\n840: \n841: | Phase | Tasks | Status | Completion |\n842: |-------|-------|--------|------------|\n843: | Phase 1: Codegen Script | T1.1-T1.8 | Pending | 0% |\n844: | Phase 2: Boilerplate | T2.1-T2.3 | Pending | 0% |\n845: | Phase 3: Directory Structure | T3.1-T3.7 | Pending | 0% |\n846: | Phase 4: Generate Clientset | T4.1-T4.10 | Pending | 0% |\n847: | Phase 5: Typed Clients | T5.1-T5.16 | Pending | 0% |\n848: | Phase 6: Fake Clients | T6.1-T6.6 | Pending | 0% |\n849: | Phase 7: Informer Factory | T7.1-T7.10 | Pending | 0% |\n850: | Phase 8: Generic Routing | T8.1-T8.6 | Pending | 0% |\n851: | Phase 9: Runtime Informers | T9.1-T9.14 | Pending | 0% |\n852: | Phase 10: Listers | T10.1-T10.11 | Pending | 0% |\n853: | Phase 11: Doc Files | T11.1-T11.4 | Pending | 0% |\n854: | Phase 12: File Count | T12.1-T12.4 | Pending | 0% |\n855: | Phase 13: Go Build | T13.1-T13.3 | Pending | 0% |\n856: | Phase 14: Integration | T14.1-T14.4 | Pending | 0% |\n857: | Phase 15: Routing Test | T15.1-T15.2 | Pending | 0% |\n858: | Phase 16: Unit Tests | T16.1-T16.5 | Pending | 0% |\n859: | Phase 17: Makefile | T17.1-T17.3 | Pending | 0% |\n860: \n861: **Total Progress: 0% Complete (0/119 t