 ## References\n76: \n77: - Spec: `changes/AR-035/spec.md`\n78: - Delta Spec: `changes/AR-035/delta-spec.md`\n79: - Proposal: `changes/AR-035/proposal.md`\n80: - Tasks: `changes/AR-035/tasks.md`\n\n(End of file - total 80 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-035 — client-go 类型客户端生成 Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-035 — client-go 类型客户端生成 |\n| Module | `client-go` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | L |\n| Stage | ST-1 |\n\n[TO BE FILLED: Provide design overview]\n\n---\n\n## Architecture\n\n### High-Level Architecture\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-035/design.md","time":{"start":1775891747889,"end":1775891747908}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775891747912,"sessionID":"ses_2849afef6ffeWBsu2Sirf6D3n3","part":{"id":"prt_d7b6591e8001b63u0znqQ4156P","messageID":"msg_d7b65756e001oVqE5t01YebvnQ","sessionID":"ses_2849afef6ffeWBsu2Sirf6D3n3","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-a108f93dbe3845a588be84b6ae4ee1a1","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-035/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-035/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-035 — client-go 类型客户端生成\n2: \n3: ## 概述\n4: \n5: | 属性 | 值 |\n6: |------|-----|\n7: | AR | AR-035 |\n8: | Module | client-go |\n9: | Language | Go |\n10: | Size | L |\n11: \n12: ---\n13: \n14: ## 1. Purpose (目的)\n15: \n16: 为 `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` API 组生成标准 Kubernetes client-go 库，使开发者能够通过类型安全的 Go 客户端与 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 自定义资源进行交互。\n17: \n18: **核心目标：**\n19: - 提供符合 Kubernetes client-go 惯例的类型化客户端\n20: - 支持完整的 CRUD 操作及 Watch/Patch 能力\n21: - 提供 Informer 和 Lister 用于控制器开发\n22: - 包含 Fake 客户端用于单元测试\n23: \n24: ---\n25: \n26: ## 2. Scope (范围)\n27: \n28: ### 2.1 In Scope\n29: \n30: | Deliverable | Description |\n31: |-------------|-------------|\n32: | Clientset | `Interface` 及 `Clientset` 实现，支持 `RuntimeV1alpha1()` 组访问器 |\n33: | Typed Client | `AgentRuntimeInterface`、`CodeInterpreterInterface`，支持 Create/Update/Delete/Get/List/Watch/Patch |\n34: | Scheme | Scheme、Codecs、ParameterCodec 注册 |\n35: | Fake Clientset | 内存模拟客户端，用于测试 |\n36: | Informer Factory | `SharedInformerFactory` 及配置选项（`WithCustomResyncConfig`、`WithTweakListOptions`、`WithNamespace`、`WithTransform`） |\n37: | Informers | AgentRuntime、CodeInterpreter 的 `SharedIndexInformer` |\n38: | Listers | 类型化 Listers，支持命名空间级别查询及 Expansion 扩展点 |\n39: \n40: ### 2.2 Out of Scope\n41: \n42: | Item | Reason |\n43: |------|--------|\n44: | API 类型定义 | 假设已在 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` 定义 |\n45: | 控制器实现 | 属于上层业务逻辑 |\n46: | REST 配置管理 | 由调用方提供 `rest.Config` |\n47: | Expansion 接口实现 | 预留空接口，不填充自定义方法 |\n48: \n49: ---\n50: \n51: ## 3. Impact Analysis (影响分析)\n52: \n53: ### 3.1 新增文件\n54: \n55: | File | Description |\n56: |------|-------------|\n57: | `clientset/versioned/clientset.go` | `Clientset`、`Interface` 及构造函数 |\n58: | `clientset/versioned/scheme/register.go` | Scheme/Codecs 构建，`AddToScheme` 注册 |\n59: | `clientset/versioned/scheme/doc.go` | 包文档 |\n60: | `clientset/versioned/fake/clientset_generated.go` | Fake clientset 实现 |\n61: | `clientset/versioned/fake/register.go` | Fake scheme wiring |\n62: | `clientset/versioned/fake/doc.go` | 包文档 |\n63: | `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/runtime_client.go` | `RuntimeV1alpha1Client`、`RuntimeV1alpha1Interface` |\n64: | `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go` | `AgentRuntimeInterface` 及实现 |\n65: | `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go` | `CodeInterpreterInterface` 及实现 |\n66: | `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/generated_expansion.go` | Expansion 接口（空） |\n67: | `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go` | 包文档 |\n68: | `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/fake/fake_runtime_client.go` | Fake runtime group client |\n69: | `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/fake/fake_agentruntime.go` | Fake AgentRuntime client |\n70: | `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/fake/fake_codeinterpreter.go` | Fake CodeInterpreter client |\n71: | `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/fake/doc.go` | 包文档 |\n72: | `informers/externalversions/factory.go` | `SharedInformerFactory` 及选项 |\n73: | `informers/externalversions/generic.go` | `GenericInformer`、`ForResource` |\n74: | `informers/externalversions/runtime/interface.go` | Group `runtime` informer 访问器 |\n75: | `informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/interface.go` | `v1alpha1` informer 访问器 |\n76: | `informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go` | AgentRuntime informer |\n77: | `informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go` | CodeInterpreter informer |\n78: | `informers/externalversions/internalinterfaces/factory_interfaces.go` | 工厂接口定义 |\n79: | `listers/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go` | `AgentRuntimeLister` 及命名空间 lister |\n80: | `listers/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go` | `CodeInterpreterLister` 及命名空间 lister |\n81: | `listers/runtime/v1alpha1/expansion_generated.go` | Lister expansion 接口 |\n82: \n83: ### 3.2 修改文件\n84: \n85: | File | Change |\n86: |------|--------|\n87: | `go.mod` | 添加 `k8s.io/code-generator` v0.34.1 依赖 |\n88: | `Makefile` | 添加 `gen-client` 目标 |\n89: | `hack/update-codegen.sh` | 新增代码生成脚本 |\n90: \n91: ### 3.3 Upstream Dependencies\n92: \n93: | Dependency | Purpose |\n94: |------------|---------|\n95: | `k8s.io/code-generator` v0.34.1 | client-go 代码生成 |\n96: | `k8s.io/client-go` | 基础客户端框架 |\n97: | `k8s.io/apimachinery` | API 类型支持 |\n98: \n99: ### 3.4 Downstream Consumers\n100: \n101: | Consumer | Usage |\n102: |----------|-------|\n103: | agentcube 控制器 | 使用 Informer/Lister 监听资源变化 |\n104: | agentcube CLI 工具 | 使用 Clientset 执行 CRUD 操作 |\n105: | 第三方集成方 | 导入 client-go 库操作自定义资源 |\n106: \n107: ---\n108: \n109: ## 4. Alternatives Considered (备选方案)\n110: \n111: ### 方案 A：手动实现客户端（已否决）\n112: \n113: **描述：** 手动编写 REST 客户端，不使用代码生成器。\n114: \n115: **优点：**\n116: - 无需维护生成脚本\n117: - 代码量更少\n118: \n119: **缺点：**\n120: - 缺乏类型安全，易出错\n121: - 无法利用 Kubernetes 生态工具（如 `controller-runtime` 的 Informer）\n122: - 测试困难，需自行实现 Fake 客户端\n123: - 不符合 Kubernetes 控制器开发惯例\n124: \n125: **结论：** 否决。不符合 Kubernetes 标准实践。\n126: \n127: ### 方案 B：使用 controller-runtime 直接生成（部分可行）\n128: \n129: **描述：** 仅使用 `controller-runtime` 的 `Builder` 模式，不生成独立 client-go。\n130: \n131: **优点：**\n132: - 更简单的控制器开发体验\n133: - 内置缓存和 Leader 选举\n134: \n135: **缺点：**\n136: - 不适合非控制器场景（如 CLI 工具）\n137: - 无法为外部用户提供类型化客户端库\n138: - 无法单独发布 client-go 供第三方使用\n139: \n140: **结论：** 作为补充方案。本项目同时支持 `controller-runtime` 和独立 client-go。\n141: \n142: ### 方案 C：标准 client-go 代码生成（采用）\n143: \n144: **描述：** 使用 `k8s.io/code-generator` 生成完整 client-go 库。\n145: \n146: **优点：**\n147: - Kubernetes 官方标准方案\n148: - 完整类型支持 + Informer + Lister + Fake\n149: - 社区广泛使用，文档丰富\n150: - 支持独立发布和版本管理\n151: \n152: **缺点：**\n153: - 需维护生成脚本\n154: - 初始代码量较大（约 25 个文件）\n155: \n156: **结论：** 采用此方案。符合项目长期维护需求。\n157: \n158: ---\n159: \n160: ## 5. Risks\n161: \n162: | Risk | Mitigation |\n163: |------|------------|\n164: | API 变更时需重新生成代码 | 使用 `make gen-client` 自动化流程 |\n165: | `k8s.io/code-generator` 版本兼容性 | 锁定 v0.34.1，定期更新依赖 |\n166: | 生成代码体积大 | 自动生成代码，可通过 `.gitattributes` 标记为 linguist-generated |\n167: | Fake 客户端行为与真实客户端不一致 | 编写集成测试验证一致性 |\n168: \n169: ---\n170: \n171: ## 6. Implementation Checklist\n172: \n173: - [ ] 创建 `hack/update-codegen.sh` 生成脚本\n174: - [ ] 配置 `go.mod` 添加 `k8s.io/code-generator` 依赖\n175: - [ ] 执行 `make gen-client` 生成代码\n176: - [ ] 验证 `Clientset` 通过 `rest.Config` 初始化\n177: - [ ] 验证 `AgentRuntimeInterface` 支持 CRUD + Watch + Patch\n178: - [ ] 验证 `CodeInterpreterInterface` 支持 CRUD + Watch + Patch\n179: - [ ] 验证 `SharedInformerFactory` 缓存和事件分发\n180: - [ ] 验证 Listers 按命名空间查询\n181: - [ ] 编写 Fake 客户端单元测试\n182: - [ ] 通过 `golangci-lint` 检查\n183: - [ ] 编写使用示例文档\n184: \n185: ---\n186: \n187: ## 7. References\n188: \n189: - Source reference: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/client-go/`\n190: - Module path: `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go`\n191: - API group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`\n192: - Generation command: `make gen-client` → `hack/update-codegen.sh` (`k8s.io/code-generator` v0.34.1, `--with-watch`)\n\n(End of file - total 192 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-035 — client-go 类型客户端生成\n\n## 概述\n\n| 属性 | 值 |\n|------|-----|\n| AR | AR-035 |\n| Module | client-go |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | L |\n\n---\n\n## 1. Purpose (目的)\n\n为 `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` API 组生成标准 Kubernetes client-go 库，使开发者能够通过类型安全的 Go 客户端与 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 自定义资源进行交互。\n\n**核心目标：**\n- 提供符合 Kubernetes client-go 惯例的类型化客户端\n- 支持完整的 CRUD 操作及 Watch/Patch 能力","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-035/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775891747892,"end":1775891747910}}}}
